#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:53
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Provide personal data</guilabel> is the first screen of the "
#| "wizard. It will prompt you for your basic account information: "
#| "<guilabel>Full name:</guilabel>, <guilabel>E-mail address</guilabel>, and "
#| "<guilabel>Password:</guilabel>. By default, the <guilabel>Find provider "
#| "settings on the Internet</guilabel> option is checked, the wizard will "
